name: starwars_xx trading cards #15: Sister & Father Fett
description:
What if...? 

What if Catholic missionaries (ha!) made their way to Mandalore? A desolate place robbed of resources and hope by war and the Empire, it would have been ripe for the folks peddling the bible to other cultures. Given what happened the last time the Church grew up around weapons, it would probably be bad for absolutely everybody else. 

In my world, it may not have actually meant weapons, but it would definitely be a sexy marriage where both players are pushed out of their comfort zones. They were always thinking about this, anyway, weren't they? 

Happy 500K, HEN!
